Study Title: Regimens Comparison for Breast Cancers of Positive Lymph Nodes
Brief Summary: To compare the efficacy and safety of EC-T and ET regimen as adjuvant treatment of breast cancer patients with positive lymph nodes
Interventions: DRUG: Epirubicin, CTX, Paclitaxel|DRUG: Epirubicin, Paclitaxel
Primary Outcome Measures: PFS, 5 years after all the recuiment
Secondary Outcome Measures: OS, 5 years after all the adjuvent treatments|Safety, Assessing for Hematology and Non-hematology toxicities, including all SAEs., 5 years after all the recruiment
Study Design: Allocation: RANDOMIZED|Intervention Model: PARALLEL|Masking: NONE|Primary Purpose: TREATMENT
Locations: Cancer Institute & Hospital. Chinese Academy of Medical Sciences, Beijing, 100021, China
